title: Modern Artist Socks Boxed Set
description:
Beat cold feet with a splash of color and a sense of humor. This set of socks transforms four modern artists into Roy Lichtenstoe, Yayoi Toesama, Feet Mondrian and Sole-Adore Dali. Made of a soft knit cotton blend. Set of 4. 

Adult uni-sex, size 10–13. 14  x 3 ½ in.
